information: fish such as dried fish, cod, herrings, king crabs and much more. Of course also salmon, fresh, frozen, smoked in best quality. Everything also in small quantities. Then we offer everything in wood, liquid gas, iron ore and milk powder and other products from milk. GOURMETAS has signed a cooperation agreement with a large milk company. This means that we can offer dairy products worldwide. We are now working on the basis of full truck/container loads. We deal in powdered dairy products such as: Whole Milk Powder, Skimmed Milk Powder, Buttermilk Powder, Whey Powder, Permeate etc., sometimes also Butter or AMF, Cheese etc. We produce mainly in Poland and Eastern Europe and cooperate with dairies worldwide, so we can also offer goods from e.g. the USA if required. We also organise transports for you - most often we offer the goods CIF named port in the country of destination. We also have a production plant (dry mix) where we produce skimmed milk mixes and fat filled milk mixes (with vegetable oil). Our production capacity is now about 700 t per month, but we are building a new production plant which should start by the end of 2021 and our production capacity will almost double. We produce both low and high protein blends. Both regular and instant products are possible. In the future, please send us your requests for dairy products from all countries. We will give you our best offer as soon as possible.
